{"tid":523044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★錢照收！iPhone 6s 送蘋果換電後卻發現電池根本沒更換","createTime":"2018-01-08T06:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T14:22:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"19c6d7027d4ddf3b4246e94ffc4ded8ff2fc43ee","tid":523044,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"舊 iPhone 用戶如果希望趁蘋果做過保換電特價期間更換電池，記得臨走前檢查清楚你的 iPhone 電池是否真的更換了。<br />\n<br />\n有網民 tenaper 投訴 Apple Store 的過保 iPhone 換電服務不周，他把他自己的 iPhone 6s 送到 Apple Store 換電去，最初員工告訴他電池沒有存貨，但蘋果檢查之後認同他那部 iPhone 6s 電池符合換電的要求，決定為他更換。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/apple-charges-29usd-for-exactly-same-iphone-battery_01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fapple-charges-29usd-for-exactly-same-iphone-battery_01.png&h=913f1e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是 tenaper<span style=\"color: red;\"> 用了 29 美元</span>（他說是 30 美元）更換了 iPhone 電池，並收到了收據之後，再用 Coconut Battery 軟件檢查電池的損耗情況，他發現電池損耗程度與舊電池一模一樣。他在利用蘋果線上人員協助之下，確認他的電池根本未更換，而且健康度良好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/01/08/apple-charges-29usd-for-exactly-same-iphone-battery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2Fapple-charges-29usd-for-exactly-same-iphone-battery%2F&d=MIfc805xsXb52afwCfAEhJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4957a426\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/01/08/apple-charges-29usd-for-exactly-same-iphone-battery/</a>"},{"pid":"b1d3ab14a6de9b68ed335f29aede00eada151ba6","tid":523044,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"